                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180506-14-victim165 t18180506-14-viclabel80"></join>. I was looking in the New Times Office window, in <placeName id="t18180506-14-crimeloc81">Fleet-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18180506-14-crimeloc81" type="placeName" value="Fleet-street"></interp>
